channel.title: I need help, i just started moparscape
channel.description:
Hello,
I just started moparscape. I have problems with logging in. What is Server IP? It says that i need to press on Cancel and then starts server. I tried this many times but it wouldn't work. Can anyone help me, please?

item.title: I need help, i just started moparscape
item.dc:creator: @slomifier slomifier
item.description:
@slomifier wrote:

like for example, try my server:

Press file in the the top left.
Press new port
Type 5555
Press OK

Than press enter, not Start Server.
Type in a desired username and password
Change the server ip to slomiscape.no-ip.info
Press Login

My servers gonna be up all day, so if you try it and it dosent work, your doing something wrong.

If it is a hamachi server use the hamachi ip supplied
and if its No-Ip (server@no-ip.info) then just put that in
